## 10. Stack technique

|Couche     |Choix                          |
|-----------|-------------------------------|
|Framework  |React                          |
|Style      |Tailwind CSS                   |
|State      |useState / useReducer          |
|Persistance|localStorage (client only)     |
|Backend    |Aucun                          |
|API externe|Aucune                         |
|Génération |JS pur (noms, stats aléatoires)|

